Example of context switching

  Authors
  -----------
  
  Hamann Denis & Delperdange Nicolas

  What is it?
  -----------

  This program will show you an example of context switching 
  and the exemple of a consummer/producer with semaphores.
  Context switching is done by IRQ.
  
  Files
  ------------  
  
  context.c
  context.h
  sem.c
  sem.h
  prodcons.c
  prodcons.h
  Makefile
  Readme (this file)


  Installation
  ------------
  
  Go into the folder containing the sources.
  Commands : 
  - To install this program : make
  - To clean : make clean
  

  Documentation
  -------------

  To use this program, run the file "main" in a terminal.
  

  
